      },
      {
        "segment": "However, we shall attempt to speak to your query for it is an helpful one in that it allows us to express once again the total unity of creation.",
        "start_offset": 391,
        "end_offset": 536,
        "start": 135.983,
        "end": 183.544
      },
      {
        "segment": "We seek the Creator upon a level of shared experience to which you are not privy and rather than surrounding ourselves in light we have become light.",
