        "end_offset": 686,
        "start": 186.004,
        "end": 234.925
      },
      {
        "segment": "Our understanding is that there is no other material except light.",
        "start_offset": 687,
        "end_offset": 753,
        "start": 237.545,
        "end": 259.606
      },
      {
        "segment": "Our rituals, as you may call them, are an infinitely subtle continuation of the balancing processes which you are now beginning to experience.",
