        "start": 262.826,
        "end": 307.727
      },
      {
        "segment": "We seek now without polarity.",
        "start_offset": 897,
        "end_offset": 926,
        "start": 311.807,
        "end": 319.947
      },
      {
        "segment": "Thus we do not invoke any power from without, for our search has become internalized as we become light/love and love/light.",
        "start_offset": 927,
        "end_offset": 1051,
        "start": 322.727,
        "end": 364.588
      },
      {
        "segment": "These are the balances we seek, the balances between compassion and wisdom which more and more allow our understanding of experience to be informed that we may come closer to the unity with the One Creator which we so joyfully seek.",
        "start_offset": 1052,
        "end_offset": 1284,
        "start": 367.128,
        "end": 438.75
      },
      {
        "segment": "Your rituals at your level of progress contain the concept of polarization and this is most central at your particular space/time.",
